trans-unit.source: Configures the <xref uid="langword_csharp_sessionPageState" name="sessionPageState" href=""></xref> section.
trans-unit.target: Konfigurerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_sessionPageState" name="sessionPageState" href=""> </xref> delen.

trans-unit.source: The SessionPageStateSection refers to the `sessionPageState` section of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: SessionPageStateSection refererer til den `sessionPageState` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The SessionPageStateSection can read and write information from and to the related section of the configuration file according to the section property <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A> whose value is <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For SessionPageStateSection kan lese og skrive informasjon fra og relaterte delen av konfigurasjonsfilen i henhold til den delen egenskapen <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>der verdien er <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition> </xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>

trans-unit.source: The SessionPageStateSection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren SessionPageStateSection skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
You obtain an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SessionPageStateSection> class by using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du hente en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SessionPageStateSection>klassen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.SessionPageStateSection>

trans-unit.source: Defines the size of the page history.
Gets or sets the size of the page history.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir størrelsen på siden loggen.

trans-unit.source: The size of the page history.
